{"id":74473,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/麦当劳蜀黍堕落史/","date":"2010-05-24T00:10:13Z","modified":"2010-05-24T20:26:47Z","title":"译者：麦当劳蜀黍堕落史","content":"<p><span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; color: black;\">麦蜀黍曾几何时人见人爱，以他的红头发，黄色的背带裤和条纹衫为标志，世界各地的孩子们见到这位和蔼可亲的小丑都开心雀跃，他们知道这位蜀黍出现的地方就会有开心乐园套餐（带玩具滴～）但是，有谁知道这个小丑背后闻者伤心见者流泪的真实故事呢？不要被灿烂的笑容所蒙蔽，伪装的背后是不为人所道的阴暗面</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; color: black;\"><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">开始的时候他是很傻很天真的，懒洋洋的靠在公园长椅上：<img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald1.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">他对警察叔叔也很尊敬</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald1a.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">他帮助老人</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald2.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">但是人们开始偶像崇拜了</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald3.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">红颜祸水也来了，不过开始还是很纯洁的</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald4.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald5.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">但是事情开始失去控制了，他开始酗酒了</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald6.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">他的健康状况令人堪忧，看他的头发就知道：</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald7.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">他开始咸猪手</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald8.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">左拥右抱的</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald9.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">再往下就更……</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald11.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">……</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">过滤了图片后 ，他对女人已经够了，开始和男人……<img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald20.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald21.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">一系列丑闻后，他的精神和身体都垮了，他成了流浪汉</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald25.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">警察们开始经常找他，一般是在他烂醉如泥后，甚至是在公园里</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald26.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald27.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">他开始报复社会，以发泄自己的不幸和愤怒，但是却找错了对象，那顾客当替罪羊</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald28.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">最后有人用枪指着他时，他开始回顾自己的一生，往日种种浮上心头，他才知道自己错了，但是已经晚了，尽管他万分怀念逝去的美好时光。<img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald29.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\">不过一切都太迟了，他死于他手，不是别人就是jack<span style=\"color: #48a2ff;\">（</span><span style=\"color: #48a2ff;\">jack也是</span><span style=\"color: #48a2ff;\">一个</span><span style=\"color: #48a2ff;\">小丑的知名形象）</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><img src=\"http://topcultured.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/ronald30.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n","author":915,"categories":[20534],"tags":[10712,8840,10711]}